title: Chrissy Teigen's Luna gets yeezy's from North and Saint | Daily Mail Online
text: comments She's not even one-years-old but it looks as though Luna Teigen already has some Valentine's admirers. Chrissy Teigen 's little girl was gifted with some Yeezy designs for Valentine's Day from Kim Kardashian 's children North and Saint on Monday. In a cute Snapchat video that the 31-year-old model uploaded, she shows an envelope that reads: Lucky girl: Chrissy Teigen's little girl was gifted with some yeezy designs for Valentine's Day from North and Saint on Monday 'Luna -Happy Valentine's Day beautiful baby girl! Lot's of love North and Saint.' In the background the Sports Illustrated model says: 'Oh my gosh Kim and Kanye my baby is doper than me, my baby's cooler than me.' The lucky toddler was gifted a pair of black yeezy sneakers. Cute gift: In a Snapchat video Chrissy says: 'Oh my gosh Kim and Kanye my baby is doper than me, my baby's cooler than me' Valentine's admirers: 'Luna -Happy Valentine's Day beautiful baby girl! Lot's of love North and Saint' She took a photo of Luna holding the shoes with the caption: 'Maybe this will help today's crankiness.' Meanwhile, Chrissy has been busy nursing her hangover from Sunday evening's Grammy awards. The model documented her drunken post-Grammy antics on Snapchat Sunday night and tweeted this morning: 'I don't feel good.' Too many shots? Meanwhile, Chrissy has been busy nursing her hangover from Sunday evening's Grammy awards It came just hours after sharing early morning video of her husband John Legend having to remove her jewelry for her after she collapsed in a giggly heap on the floor when they got home from the post-awards show party at Hollywood's Chateau Marmont. The Sports Illustrated beauty also shared a pic on Snapchat showing her breakfast of champions - hash browns with brown sauce. It's not known if it helped her any since she's already tweeted that she had tried drinking a soda but couldn't taste it.
